---
interface Props {
  totalCount: number;
  catalogPath: string;
  primaryPath: string | null;
  portalPath: string;
}

const { totalCount, catalogPath, primaryPath, portalPath } = Astro.props;
---

<section class="hero-panel">
  <p class="eyebrow">index.hagicode.com/data</p>
  <div class="hero-copy">
    <div>
      <p class="hero-kicker">Legacy Data Mirror</p>
      <h1>HagiCode Index Data</h1>
    </div>
    <p class="hero-lede">
      原首页内容已迁移到这里。面向程序直连，也给维护者一个能快速核对目录、来源与同步状态的数据镜像页。
    </p>
  </div>
  <dl class="hero-metrics" aria-label="目录概览">
    <div>
      <dt>已发布条目</dt>
      <dd>{totalCount}</dd>
    </div>
    <div>
      <dt>页面职责</dt>
      <dd>镜像</dd>
    </div>
    <div>
      <dt>返回路径</dt>
      <dd>门户</dd>
    </div>
  </dl>
  <div class="hero-actions">
    <a class="button button-primary" href={portalPath}>
      返回站点门户
    </a>
    {primaryPath ? (
      <a class="button button-tertiary" href={primaryPath} target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">
        打开首个索引
      </a>
    ) : (
      <span class="button button-disabled" aria-disabled="true">
        暂无可用索引
      </span>
    )}
    <a class="button button-secondary" href={catalogPath} target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">
      查看目录 JSON
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
